OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773979416
OL,3,CWhy Trump's Iran war may be Starmer's
OL,4,Clast chance
OL,6,FIt may not be obvious yet, but the
OL,7,Fscale of the threat to our security
OL,8,Fand our prosperity caused by Donald
OL,9,FTrump's offensive against Iran is
OL,10,Fhighly likely in many voters minds,
OL,11,Fperhaps in most voters' minds, to wipe
OL,12,Fout anger or disappointment with him
OL,13,Fafter 18 months of tax rises, U-turns
OL,14,Fand Peter Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773979416
OL,3,CWhy Trump's Iran war may be Starmer's
OL,4,Clast chance
OL,6,FSo, as oil and gas prices soar, as
OL,7,Fshortages are likely to emerge in
OL,8,Feverything from petrol to semi
OL,9,Fconductors, one question is whether he
OL,10,Fwill be able to protect living
OL,11,Fstandards and jobs, without putting
OL,12,Fundue pressure on the public finances.
OL,14,FThe war also has dramatic
OL,15,Framifications for public spending
OL,16,Fchoices - because what the public has
OL,17,Fwitnessed, if they didn't know
OL,18,Falready, is that our military is
OL,19,Fchronically under-resourced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773979416
OL,3,CWhy Trump's Iran war may be Starmer's
OL,4,Clast chance
OL,6,FSo, his ten-year project to replenish
OL,7,Fthe armed forces and restructure
OL,8,Ftowards unmanned (drone) warfare is
OL,9,Falmost comically too long, and the
OL,10,Ffailure yet to publish his promised
OL,11,Fdefence investment plan is almost
OL,12,Fscandalous.
OL,14,FWith Angela Rayner warming up for a
OL,15,Ftilt at his job, Starmer has a last
OL,16,Fchance to redeem himself in whether or
OL,17,Fnot he wastes the economic and
OL,18,Fgeopolitical crisis or just looks like
OL,19,Fa bystander.
OL,26,@pD@RpmpD@Xpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
