PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773979416
OL,3,CWhy Trump's Iran war may be Starmer's
OL,4,Clast chance
OL,6,FTrump may say he is no Churchill. And
OL,7,Falthough Churchill's ability to tell
OL,8,Fstories about the road to future
OL,9,Fvictories might be helpful at the
OL,10,Fmoment - and on the revealed evidence,
OL,11,Fsuch narrative power will never be
OL,12,Favailable to Starmer - Churchill's
OL,13,Fnotorious incompetence with money and
OL,14,Fshambolism would not be ideal for a
OL,15,Fnation struggling to convince
OL,16,Fcreditors its debts are sustainable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
