PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773979416
OL,3,CWhy Trump's Iran war may be Starmer's
OL,4,Clast chance
OL,6,FWhat's required - who is required - is
OL,7,Fa PM who can reassure with calm,
OL,8,Fdogged crisis management. There was a
OL,9,Ftime when that seemed to be his skill
OL,10,Fset. We'll find out too soon if that
OL,11,Fwas an illusion.
